cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.NI, cs.SY 

This paper focuses on the cybersecurity concerns of smart buildings, specifically the integration of consumer IoT devices with operational technology controllers and actuators. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
